headline: Camden Property Trust Announces Dual Listing on NYSE Texas
summary: HOUSTON, December 18, 2025--Camden Property Trust (NYSE:CPT) (the "Company") announced today the dual listing of its common stock on NYSE Texas, the newly launched, fully electronic equities exchange headquartered in Dallas, Texas. The Company will maintain its primary listing on the New York Stock Exchange and trade under the same ticker symbol "CPT" on NYSE Texas.
